										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you use Windows for your desktop there&#8217;s a handy little tool for WordPress comment management &#8211; <a href="http://www.deanlee.cn/projects/wp-comments-notifiera-wordpress-comments-notifier/">wp-comments-notifier</a>.  It uses the WordPress XML-RPC APIs to check for new comments and manage them.  How-To Geek has a <a href="http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/17431/manage-your-wordpress-blog-comments-from-your-windows-desktop/">great post describing how to use it</a>.</p>
